drm/tve200: Use drm_gem_fb_create() and drm_gem_fb_prepare_fb()

drm_fb_cma_create() and drm_fb_cma_prepare_fb() are just wrappers now,
use drm_gem_fb_create() and drm_gem_fb_prepare_fb() directly.

